## Code Standards

### Core Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React 19, TypeScript
- **Data & Routing**: TanStack Suite (Router, Query, Table, Start)
- **State Management**: Zustand
- **UI/UX**: Shadcn UI, Radix Primitives, Tailwind CSS
